msgid ""
"Starts a new ``Thread`` that runs ``method`` on object ``instance`` with "
"``userdata`` passed as an argument. The ``priority`` of the ``Thread`` "
"can be changed by passing a value from the :ref:`Priority "
"<enum_Thread_Priority>` enum."
msgstr ""

